## 2. WebGPU Browser Support (2026)

| Browser | Status | Min Version |
|---|---|---|
| Chrome | Stable, enabled by default | 113+ desktop; 121+ Android 12+ |
| Edge | Stable | 113+ |
| Firefox | Stable (Windows); macOS ARM in 141+ | 141+ |
| Safari | Stable | macOS Tahoe 26 / iOS 26 only |
| Others | No | — |

**Global support: ~82% as of 2026.** `navigator.gpu` check is reliable — no origin trial needed in Chrome/Edge/modern Firefox. Demo must not fail if undefined (scripted fallback carries the full happy path for CI/headless).

