## 3. Recharts (Analytics.jsx) — Exact Imports

```bash
npm install recharts
```

```js
import {
  BarChart, Bar, XAxis, YAxis, CartesianGrid, Tooltip,
  ResponsiveContainer, PieChart, Pie, Cell, Legend
} from "recharts";
```

**Bar chart (call volume, 7 days):**
```jsx
<ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height={200}>
  <BarChart data={callVolumeData}>
    <CartesianGrid strokeDasharray="3 3" stroke="#CCFBF1" />
    <XAxis dataKey="day" tick={{ fontSize: 11, fill: "#64748B" }} />
    <YAxis tick={{ fontSize: 11, fill: "#64748B" }} />
    <Tooltip />
    <Bar dataKey="calls" fill="#0D9488" radius={[4,4,0,0]} />
  </BarChart>
</ResponsiveContainer>
```

**Doughnut (intent breakdown):**
```jsx
<PieChart width={180} height={180}>
  <Pie data={intentData} cx={90} cy={90}
    innerRadius={50} outerRadius={80}
    dataKey="value" paddingAngle={3}>
    {intentData.map((_, i) => <Cell key={i} fill={INTENT_COLORS[i]} />)}
  </Pie>
  <Tooltip />
</PieChart>
```
`INTENT_COLORS = ["#0D9488", "#059669", "#EF4444"]` (Book / FAQ / Escalate)

