## 5. Healthcare Voice AI Conversation Scripts (EN + ES)

### Inbound — Greeting
```
EN: "Thank you for calling TeleHealthy. I'm your AI health assistant. How can I help you today?"
ES: "Gracias por llamar a TeleHealthy. Soy su asistente de salud virtual. ¿En qué puedo ayudarle hoy?"
```

### Intent Detection Keywords
```
BOOK:     schedule, appointment, book, see doctor, visit, available, slot, reschedule, cancel
FAQ:      hours, open, insurance, accept, telehealth, online, location, address, new patient, eligibility, cost
ESCALATE: emergency, crisis, suicidal, prescription, refill, medication, urgent, chest pain, hurt
```
Threshold: if WebLLM confidence JSON < 0.45 → auto-escalate regardless of keyword.

### Booking Flow (EN)
```
Step 1 — Confirm intent:  "I can help you schedule an appointment. Are you a new patient or an existing patient?"
Step 2 — Collect name:    "May I have your full name please?"
Step 3 — Collect reason:  "What's the reason for your visit today?"
                          [Options shown as pills: Initial Eval | Follow-up | Medication Review | Telehealth Consult]
Step 4 — Date/time:       "What date and time works best for you? We have availability Monday through Friday, 8 AM to 6 PM."
Step 5 — Confirm:         "I've scheduled you for [DATE] at [TIME] with [PROVIDER]. You'll receive an SMS confirmation shortly."
Step 6 — Close:           "Is there anything else I can help you with today?"
```

### FAQ Responses (EN)
```
hours:       "We're open Monday–Friday 8 AM to 6 PM and Saturday 9 AM to 1 PM. After-hours, you can leave a message."
insurance:   "We accept Blue Cross BlueShield, Aetna, Cigna, UnitedHealth, Medicare, and Molina Healthcare. Would you like to verify your specific plan?"
telehealth:  "Yes, we offer secure video appointments for established patients. You'll need a device with a camera. Telehealth slots are available daily."
new patient: "Welcome! New patient intake appointments are 60 minutes. We'll collect your insurance info and medical history at that visit."
location:    "Our main clinic is at 4820 Wellness Blvd, Suite 200. Parking is validated in the attached garage."
```

### FAQ Responses (ES)
```
hours:       "Estamos abiertos de lunes a viernes de 8 AM a 6 PM y sábados de 9 AM a 1 PM."
insurance:   "Aceptamos Blue Cross BlueShield, Aetna, Cigna, UnitedHealth, Medicare y Molina Healthcare."
telehealth:  "Sí, ofrecemos citas de video seguras para pacientes establecidos."
new patient: "¡Bienvenido! Las citas de nuevo paciente duran 60 minutos."
```

### Escalation Script
```
Low-confidence trigger (<0.45):
"I want to make sure you get the right support. Let me connect you with one of our care coordinators right away. Please hold."

Clinical urgency trigger (crisis/prescription keywords):
"I'm connecting you immediately to our on-call clinical team. Please stay on the line."

Warm transfer UI state: transcript shows "[AI ASSISTANT] Transferring to Care Coordinator..." + contact card + hold music indicator
```

