## 8. Scaffold Pointer (Vite + React 18)

```bash
# From upwork-runs/telehealthy/
npm create vite@latest demo-src -- --template react
cd demo-src
npm install recharts
# web-llm loaded via CDN ESM — no npm install
```

**vite.config.js:**
```js
import { defineConfig } from "vite";
import react from "@vitejs/plugin-react";
export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [react()],
  base: "/demos/telehealthy/",
  build: {
    outDir: "../../../../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/telehealthy",
    emptyOutDir: true
  }
});
```

**Google Fonts in index.html:**
```html
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
```

**Deploy:**
```bash
npm run build  # outputs to ../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/telehealthy/
```

