## handoff
- produced: WebLLM CDN URL + model ID (q4f16_1 override from plan's q4f32_1) + init pattern; WebGPU support matrix; recharts exact imports; 8 CRM mock contacts with scriptVars; full EN/ES conversation scripts for all 3 flows; Vapi/Retell UI conventions (bubbles, confidence bar, waveform, intent badge, pipeline viz); analytics seed data; Vite scaffold commands
- decisions: model changed to `Llama-3.2-1B-Instruct-q4f16_1-MLC` (~700MB vs ~1.3GB) — demo-builder MUST use this ID not q4f32_1; CDN ESM via dynamic `import()` inside useWebLLM.js; recharts for both bar + doughnut; scripted fallback is deterministic and carries all 3 intents fully
- next needs: demo-builder implements `useWebLLM.js` with lazy dynamic import + progress state; InboundCall.jsx uses conversation scripts + waveform animation + confidence bar + pipeline viz; Analytics.jsx uses recharts with seed data; OutboundDialer.jsx uses crmContacts with scriptVars for dynamic script generation; all 12 files follow plan's file list exactly
- risks: WebLLM model download still ~700-800MB — lazy-load behind button + scripted fallback must cover full happy path (confirmed for CI/headless); WebGPU unavailable in headless Playwright — scripted path is the deploy-test path
